  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/5fdf26f60dae7ec73aa4525e04789327.avif?t=1751893589\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br>With each step, you'll face choices that can lead to untold riches or dire consequences. Will you risk it all to rise above?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/a3ce644d7aa6a9aa1cd84025ac688b31.poster.avif?t=1751893589\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/a3ce644d7aa6a9aa1cd84025ac688b31.webm?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/a3ce644d7aa6a9aa1cd84025ac688b31.mp4?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/50fc6da32875d10f1a406626dbd958a9.avif?t=1751893589\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br>Turn the odds in your favor by capturing defeated enemies and adding them to your deck. Harness their unique abilities and unleash havoc upon your foes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/cf1eb499e750c42ef5cccceb0af10e86.poster.avif?t=1751893589\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/cf1eb499e750c42ef5cccceb0af10e86.webm?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/cf1eb499e750c42ef5cccceb0af10e86.mp4?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/95210d5267dbf12b3be913dd3ed74a8e.avif?t=1751893589\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br>As you select both a character and a loyal pet for your expedition, the choices you make extend beyond mere aesthetics. Align yourself with a single clan out of three and double down on a single clan’s strengths, or pair two distinct clans for an edge in different types of encounters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/9141db756dac7c085c8a4ae1c55a948f.poster.avif?t=1751893589\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/9141db756dac7c085c8a4ae1c55a948f.webm?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/9141db756dac7c085c8a4ae1c55a948f.mp4?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/f7f8e6d4bd0022f4548b77612429d683.avif?t=1751893589\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br>Meet a cast of eccentric characters lurking within the tower's shadows. From enigmatic elves to mischievous robots, every encounter adds a touch of unpredictability to your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/a9be1f7e2b9073e9739b91725e9e6030.poster.avif?t=1751893589\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/a9be1f7e2b9073e9739b91725e9e6030.webm?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/a9be1f7e2b9073e9739b91725e9e6030.mp4?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/de9d078901f13f08f9f06c6edc227dd1.avif?t=1751893589\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br>Ascend the tower, not just physically, but also in power. Unlock new orbs, uncover artifacts, and enhance your characters with a robust skill tree system to shape your personal playstyle and conquer the tower's mysteries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/51dcb6a153bba354514c6b3fe3c2efa4.poster.avif?t=1751893589\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/51dcb6a153bba354514c6b3fe3c2efa4.webm?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/51dcb6a153bba354514c6b3fe3c2efa4.mp4?t=1751893589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/68bb88e5b604c64363161aca8d0c21d4.avif?t=1751893589\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br>With each ascent, the tower reshapes its halls and challenges. Adapt and strategize as you climb higher, facing new challenges at every floor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/67859c413760f30f66b11dbde3bf04f6.avif?t=1751893589\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>150+ Unique Orbs:</strong> Amass a collection of orbs, featuring both clan-exclusive and neutral choices.<br></li><li> <strong>Varied Partners:</strong> Randomized characters and pets, each with distinct traits, stats, and visuals.<br></li><li> <strong>Three Clans:</strong> Choose among three clans, and fuse primary and secondary clans to create varied character builds.<br></li><li> <strong>Empower Your Orbs:</strong> Choose from 20 enhancements to fortify your orbs, refining your gameplay approach.<br></li><li> <strong>Fight 30 Distinct Foes:</strong> Confront a roster of 30 distinct enemy types, each with unique behaviors and challenges.<br></li><li> <strong>Adapt with Enemy Resources:</strong> Seize enemies, their tools, and weapons to bolster your deck's strength and versatility.<br></li><li> <strong>Diverse Artifact Collection:</strong> Stumble upon 30 distinct artifacts, bestowing either empowering enhancements or daunting curses.<br></li><li> <strong>Dynamic Encounters:</strong> Experience random events, interact with shopkeepers, and engage in interactions between battles.</li></ul><br>Are you ready to challenge the shadowy depths of Gamble Tower, where every step can be decided by the roll of a dice? The ultimate gambit awaits – for only the boldest gamblers will emerge victorious.",
